Articles.Content: Hey, Just wanted to say hello to all the Kerbanaughts out there and share my first Mun landing. (rather proud of that) Though I think Bob knows that he ain\'t coming home..

Welcome to the KSP Forums!

Happy Launching!

Arrr!

Capt\'n Skunky

You landed without gear? Wow.

That RCS isn\'t enough to get back, is it?

Welcome
Thanks for the welcome! Well I did have liquid fuel engine there.. but I hit the mun a little too hard I guess.
